tips:["Use present perfect: 'I have visited...'","Use past continuous: 'I was walking when...'","Use comparatives: 'more interesting than'","Use conditionals: 'If I had..., I would...'","Use reported speech: 'He said that...'","Use passive voice: 'It was built in 1990'"],
